<section id="fs">
  <title>fs</title>
  <para>Format style
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string<?oxy_custom_end?>,
      <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><code>fs_fs</code><?oxy_custom_end?>
    - allows most structural and inline
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>JLIFF<?oxy_custom_end?> core
    elements to convey basic formatting information using a predefined subset of HTML formatting
    elements (for example, HTML elements names like &lt;script&gt; are not included). It enables the
    generation of HTML pages or snippets for preview and review purposes. If additional style
    information is needed, the <glossterm>optional</glossterm>
    <olink targetdoc="subFs.xml" targetptr="subFs"><code>fs_subFs</code></olink> string is
    provided.</para>
